akka.actor.typed

Class AbstractExtensionSetup<T extends Extension>

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.actor.setup.Setup
      • akka.actor.typed.ExtensionSetup<T>
        • akka.actor.typed.AbstractExtensionSetup<T>

  • public abstract class AbstractExtensionSetup<T extends Extension>
extends ExtensionSetup<T>
    Scala 2.11 API: Each extension typically provide a concrete ExtensionSetup that can be used in ActorSystemSetup when starting the ActorSystem to replace the default implementation of the extension. Intended for tests that need to replace extension with stub/mock implementations.
